Imagine a version of tetris that you wouldn't want to play, but make it worse. 
That's the goal here. 

I wrote this as a learning project, and as it turns out I had a lot to learn.
This really needs a lot of polish but it isn't going to get it because in retrospect I'd 
end up re-writing it. Saving because I want something to look back on. 

To play, clone it and the open index.html in your browser. 

Arrow right and left move the piece, space rotates. Down accelerates to the bottom. 

Don't play it.